did.abstract: Pornography magazines featuring men, mostly the first and only volumes of a title.

scopecontent.head: COLLECTION DESCRIPTION
scopecontent.p: Pornography magazines featuring men, mostly the first and only volumes of a title. Most show male models with other male models, directed at a gay male audience. A few magazines present male models as for a heterosexual female audience.
